            "title": "$100 Invested In ICICI Bank 20 Years Ago Would Be Worth This Much Today",
            "description": "<div><div class=\"sc-fmEAfK gfWgFw\"><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">ICICI Bank <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NYSE\" data-ticker=\"IBN\" style=\"display:inline-block\">IBN</span> has outperformed the market over the past 20 years by 1.92% on an annualized basis producing an average annual return of 10.39%. Currently, ICICI Bank has a market capitalization of $117.93 billion. </p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>Buying $100 In IBN:</strong> If an investor had bought $100 of IBN stock 20 years ago, it would be worth <strong>$718.60</strong> today based on a price of $33.05 for IBN at the time of writing.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><div class=\"sc-gwChKv hMRcLH\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\"><div class=\"font-semibold\">Trending Investment Opportunities</div><div class=\"flex items-end justify-end\"><div class=\"text-right text-sm bg-gray-200 rounded px-2 py-1\">Advertisement</div></div></div><div class=\"cta-stacked GalleryCarousel_splide_slidewrap__zHpTC\"><div class=\"sc-FhnSQ kphHWf carousel-container\"><div aria-label=\"Carousel\" class=\"splide\"><div class=\"splide-track-wrapper\"><div class=\"splide__track\"><ul class=\"splide__list\"><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li><li class=\"splide__slide\"><div class=\"sc-ePKekS icxejb call-to-action vertical vertical\"></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"carousel-pagination\"><div class=\"splide__arrows\"><button class=\"sc-gUMLBR dFGHQt primary md splide__arrow splide__arrow--prev page-left-button\" type=\"button\"><span><div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"leading-none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" style=\"height:1em;width:1em\" viewbox=\"0 0 320 51